headline: Lindsay (LNN) Surpasses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Lindsay (LNN) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +30.88% and +4.60%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
